    D. How consumer confidence effects the stock market:<br>
1. If people have no confidence in the quarterly reports and earnings statements that come out then they withdraw thier money from thier Stock portfolios and place it somewhere safer..EX:Bonds, Cd's Moneymarket, mutualfunds(as they can't hold more than 5% of one stock, this offers a safety net for people who want stocks but not all the risk) there are several others but I dont want to go to far over peoples heads....Now as people pull thier cash from these corporations thier stock prices plumit leaving them with out the capital to R&amp;D(research and developement), they will have production overstock..aka excess inventory..as people watch thier 401k's shrink and dont spend...Until people have faith again in Corporate America this will be the case..all you will hear about is consumer confidence as it is the single most important factor at this time<br>
